      "webPublicationDate":"2013-10-17T02:15:00Z",
      "webTitle":"Morrissey hits back at NME and the judge who called him 'devious'",
      "webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/music/2013/oct/17/morrissey-autobiography-hits-back-judge-nme",
